                                "byte_start": 81775,
                                "byte_stop": 119600,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 91-6194, Crosby against the United States will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.447,
                        "stop": 87.223,
